{"tid":1132864,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳蘇B狂鬧馬迪爾態度差","createTime":"2019-04-30T15:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T17:13:16.000Z","uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0928e68712f5a1c2adc439d4965db7c0d68dbff9","tid":1132864,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:25:18.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】曼聯上仗主場被車路士逼和1:1，事隔多天，英國傳媒陸續爆出當日更衣室的情況。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》指，領隊蘇斯克查（Ole Gunnar Solskjaer）不滿前鋒安東尼馬迪爾的態度，在一眾球員面前將之怒罵，更把他放在後備席，當射手拉舒福特因傷退下火線時，也不選擇這名法國國腳，以鮮有表現的翼鋒阿歷斯山齊士入替。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，馬迪爾賽前已經被球迷批評，在熱身時只站著冷眼旁觀，不投入比賽。他今季場均跑動距離，亦是紅魔前線球員中最少，只得8.45公里，就連山神也有9.56公里。<br />\n<br />\n至於英國《太陽報》則報道，在上半場派膠令左閘馬高斯阿朗素攻入扳平一球的門將迪基亞，半場在更衣室內向隊友道歉。消息人士指：「他爆粗說『我搞垮了』，領隊叫他忘記這事，專注下半場。」"},{"pid":"332a4dfd6dbf9bd9d8d3a5eb8ac0d6af6715bef0","tid":1132864,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"爹地一早話要賣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a2bec5153f1c625abb5daa637f70c42a206657","tid":1132864,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/paulsherlock69/status/1122594681345511426/video/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fpaulsherlock69%2Fstatus%2F1122594681345511426%2Fvideo%2F1&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=84387b8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/paulsherlock69/status/1122594681345511426/video/1</a>"},{"pid":"0eabaef6b06856126a596bb784af05ed725617b2","tid":1132864,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"332a4dfd6dbf9bd9d8d3a5eb8ac0d6af6715bef0","tid":1132864,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"爹地一早話要賣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hk